{{Infobox organization |name = Miss Supertalent |image = MissSupertalent bw.png |image_border = |size = 250 px |caption = |map = |msize = |mcaption = |motto = Talent and Beauty Reign Supreme |formation = 2011 |type = [[Beauty Pageant]], [[Talent Search]] |headquarters = [[Seoul]] |location = [[South Korea]] |language = [[English language|English]] |leader_title = President |leader_name = Lawrence Choi |affiliations = [[Suta Group]] }}
The '''Miss Supertalent of the World''' is a half yearly high-profile media event with a unique format showcasing fashion as well as talent organized and produced by [[Suta Group]]. It was created as an international entertainment collaboration showcasing acting, singing, choreography and modeling with the focus on talent and beauty. Supertalent [[Fashion Week]] and Supertalent [[World Record]] are units events of Miss Supertalent of the World.<ref>{{cite news|title=50 Global Superstars To Compete in Miss SuperTalent of the World 2016|url=http://www.retailnews.asia/50-global-superstars-to-compete-in-miss-supertalent-of-the-world-2016/|publisher=Retail News|date=February 27, 2016|accessdate=December 8, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Milett Figueroa se corona Miss Supertalent of the World 2016|url=http://rpp.pe/famosos/chollywood/milett-figueroa-se-corona-miss-supertalent-of-the-world-2016-noticia-1014145/|publisher=RPP|date=December 3, 2016|accessdate=December 8, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Natalie Stejskalova wins Miss Supertalent World 2016|url=http://beautypageants.indiatimes.com/others/Natalie-Stejskalova-wins-Miss-Supertalent-World-2016/articleshow/52277576.cms|publisher=India Times|date=March 15, 2016|accessdate=December 8, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Miss Supertalent 2016: Milett Figueroa recibe duras críticas por desafinar|url=http://www.americatv.com.pe/noticias/espectaculos/miss-supertalent-2016-milett-figueroa-recibe-duras-criticas-desafinar-n256756|publisher=America TV|date=December 5, 2016|accessdate=December 8, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Supermiss Paulína Pélyová: Vyhrála světovou soutěž krásy díky Blesku|url=http://www.blesk.cz/clanek/celebrity-ceske-celebrity/435630/supermiss-paulina-pelyova-vyhrala-svetovou-soutez-krasy-diky-blesku.html|publisher=CZECH NEWS CENTER|date=December 7, 2016|accessdate=December 17, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Novobančanka Paulína Pélyová (24) úspešná v celosvetovej súťaži krásy: Takto sa tešila z prvenstva (FOTO)|url=http://nasziar.sme.sk/c/20405491/novobancanka-paulina-pelyova-24-uspesna-v-celosvetovej-sutazi-krasy-takto-sa-tesila-z-prvenstva-foto.html|publisher=Petit Press, a.s.|date=December 9, 2016|accessdate=December 18, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Milett Figueroa ganó el Miss Supertalent of the World 2016|url=http://elcomercio.pe/luces/moda/miss-supertalent-2016-milett-figueroa-final-vivo-noticia-1950933|publisher=RED EL COMERCIO|date=December 4, 2016|accessdate=December 18, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Estos son los ostentosos premios que ganó Milett Figueroa en el Miss Supertalent 2016|url=http://larepublica.pe/espectaculos/827386-estos-son-los-ostentosos-premios-que-gano-milett-figueroa-en-el-miss-supertalent-2016|publisher=Grupo La República Publicaciones|date=December 3, 2016|accessdate=December 18, 2016}}</ref>
