==''Supertalent Fashion Week''== Miss Supertalent Organization had launched a series of spin-off shows 'Supertalent [[Fashion Week]]' which showed the clips of Miss Supertalent Contestants's Fashion Week from all over the world. The event is three days long per season and held twice a year at the [[Korea International Exhibition Center]], [[Daegu]] Textile Complex, [[Incheon International Airport]]<ref>{{cite news|title=슈퍼탤런트, 오늘은 패션모델 '킨텍스 패션쇼'|url=http://www.stardailynews.co.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=146093|publisher=Star Daily|date=May 12, 2017|accessdate=November 10, 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=아바타TV ‘미스 슈퍼탤런트 2017’ 현장 생중계|url=http://www.e2news.com/news/articleView.html?idxno=102707|publisher=e2news|date=October 12, 2017|accessdate=November 10, 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=[대구소식]대구도시철도, 디트로 패션쇼 개최 등|url=http://www.newsis.com/view/?id=NISX20171020_0000123684&cID=10810&pID=10800|publisher=Newsis|date=October 21, 2017|accessdate=November 10, 2017}}</ref>, [[South Korea]], [[Eiffel Tower]], [[Galeries Lafayette]]<ref>{{cite news|title=슈퍼탤런트 시즌 11, 라파에트 갤러리와 파리 오페라좌를 더욱 눈부시게~|url=http://www.sportsseoul.com/news/read/699670|publisher=Sports Seoul=November 10, 2018|accessdate=November 10, 2018}}</ref>, [[Paris]], [[Jungfrau]]<ref>{{cite news|title=알프스의 비경 융프라우에서 패션쇼를 펼친 슈퍼탤런트 참가자들, 아이거 앞에서 신고식을~|url=http://www.sportsseoul.com/news/read/697515|publisher=Sports Seoul=November 5, 2018|accessdate=November 12, 2018}}</ref>, [[Schilthorn]]<ref>{{cite news|title=슈퍼탤런트 시즌 11, 알프스를 런웨이로 만들어버려~|url=http://www.sportsseoul.com/news/read/697888|publisher=Sports Seoul=November 6, 2018|accessdate=November 12, 2018}}</ref>, [[Switzerland]]
